A fruit is a kind of value. An apple, a pear and an orange are fruits.

To begin:
	showme the number of fruits;
	showme the fruit after the pear;
	showme the fruit after the orange;
	showme the fruit before the pear;
	showme the fruit before the apple;
	showme the first value of fruit;
	showme the last value of fruit;
	say "[last value of fruit]";